    "Body": " You will use your talents in outside sales to make Blockchain technology transform and secure business processes for our customers. Chainyard is an emerging leader in Blockchain technology and application delivery, working with major corporations using both Ethereum and Hyperledger Fabric. We accelerate the development of Blockchain infrastructure, middleware, and decentralized applications. Our teams bring extensive experience in architecting, designing, building, testing, securing and operating complex distributed systems to help early adopters of Blockchain technology succeed. We work with multiple Blockchain technologies and have a specific focus on Hyperledger Fabric and its ecosystem. Chainyard??\u201e??, an IT People Company is looking for a Technical Sales Executive to work with our talented Blockchain team in Morrisville, NC. You will work to identify companies that leverage service providers and establish a trusted advisor relationship with the key stakeholders to align their needs with our services. In this role, you??\u20ac???ll focus on partnering with top companies to build and carry out a sales strategy that guides accelerated bookings focused on application architecture, design, development, maintenance and support. You will use your business and technical acumen to demonstrate thought leadership and execution efficiency throughout the sales process. You will collaborate with your peers within the company to identify opportunities, develop strategies, draft proposals, respond to RFPs, share best practices and help drive the company forward. Your responsibilities include: Develop and generate new business through referrals, phone calls, in-person meetings, presentations and networking at local association events, conferences and technical events. Develop and grow your own client base using both inside and outside sales techniques by marketing our services for emerging technologies to clients demonstrating how we can add significant business value. Working and collaborating with our experienced team to present best of breed emerging technology solutions to our clients. Write and get approval for proposals that align customers needs with our services to gain client alignment and acceptance. Working closely with clients to maintain the highest level of customer satisfaction. Responsible for concurrently moving multiple opportunities through sales process: prospecting, discovery, meetings, proposal development/demonstration, selection, negotiation and close. Set and achieve revenue goals that grow the business. Complete all administrative tasks and other duties as needed in a timely manner Job Requirements: Minimum 5 years of Consulting Services, SaaS Platform or Technical Software Product Sales is required. Must have excellent communication, presentation skills, interpersonal skills, and business and technology acumen. Hunter mentality is essential. Business development and account management skills are required. Utilize your proven closing skills and the ability to build strong client relationships. Possess a track record of growing a customer base and meeting/exceeding revenue targets and organizational goals. Must be able to work with clients to clarify and define requirements to develop proposals in alignment to their needs. Must have ability to multi-task and perform at an elevated level in a fast-paced dynamic environment. Must be collaborative, team-oriented with ability and willingness to help continue to grow the business to new highs. ", 
